        "text": "=You are a recruiter AI. Evaluate this candidate.\\n\\nROLE: {{ $json.body.role }}\\n\\nCV:\\n<<<CV>>>\\n{{ $json.body.cv_text }}\\n<<<END>>>\\n\\nReturn ONLY JSON:\\n{\\n  \\\"score\\\": number,\\n  \\\"recommendation\\\": \\\"SHORTLIST\\\" | \\\"REJECT\\\",\\n  \\\"strengths\\\": [],\\n  \\\"gaps\\\": [],\\n  \\\"summary\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n}",
